            , depos'd that she saw her a dying, and that she lay on a cold brick Floor. Mr. Vaughan, Mr. Sherword, Surgeons, and 
               <persName id="t17211206-18-person160">
                  Edw 
                  Lampton 
               <interp inst="t17211206-18-person160" type="surname" value="Lampton"></interp>
