                     <interp inst="t17211206-18-person160" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , Servant to Mr. Vaughan, depos'd, that there was an Inflamation in the Deceased's Lungs, occasion'd by her hard drinking, and the cold place she lay in, which in their Opinion caus'd her Death; and that the Wounds she receiv'd were not mortal. The Jury found him <rs id="t17211206-18-verdict89" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17211206-18-verdict89" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
